{"tid":2496921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國最新失業率降至4.9%　出乎市場預料","createTime":"2021-04-20T06:59:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T07:16:08.000Z","uid":24660,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"344884bdc52ab7450203e0037959153ace934c4b","tid":2496921,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T06:59:40.000Z","msg":"英國最新失業率降至4.9%，出乎市場預料，市場原本估計升至5.1%。<br />\n<br />\n英國至2月止3個月，按照國際勞工組織標準(ILO)的失業率為4.9%，較之前低0.1個百分點。3月申領失業金人數按月增加1.01萬人。<br />\n<br />\n期內，平均周薪按年增加4.5%，增幅低於預期的4.8%，不包括奬金的周薪按年增加4.4%，亦好過預期。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1586720-20210420.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1586720-20210420.htm&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuFpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=8253689f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1586720-20210420.htm&h=4e4e1649\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1586720-20210420.htm</a>"},{"pid":"fd62d2fcf2455743bbaea3082cdbedeeaae83f06","tid":2496921,"uid":39750,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T07:01:25.000Z","msg":"好過香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b08fc406aa9c10cc2ffb42ebf203d3be5829c3f5","tid":2496921,"uid":237459,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T07:01:46.000Z","msg":"BORIS <br />\n<br />\nBREXIT"},{"pid":"553c3f8ccb9babf7acc77b35b8e692fe6fd22498","tid":2496921,"uid":269864,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"344884bdc52ab7450203e0037959153ace934c4b","tid":2496921,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T06:59:40.000Z","msg":"英國最新失業率降至4.9%，出乎市場預料，市場原本估計升至5.1%。<br />\n<br />\n英國至2月止3個月，按照國際勞工組織標準(ILO)的失業率為4.9%，較之前低0.1個百分點。3月申領失業金人數按月增加1.01萬人。<br />\n<br />\n期內，平均周薪按年增加4.5%，增幅低於預期的4.8%，不包括奬金的周薪按年增加4.4%，亦好過預期。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https: